# Hermes Agent Self-Evolution README

# Hermes Agent Self-Evolution

**Evolutionary self-improvement for [[hermes-agent-complete-guide]].**

Uses DSPy + GEPA (Genetic-Pareto Prompt Evolution) to automatically evolve and optimize Hermes Agent's skills, tool descriptions, system prompts, and code.

